        <mxCell id="a-e9" edge="1" parent="1" source="a-cons" target="a-ext-kb" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;html=1;exitX=1;exitY=0.5;entryX=0;entryY=0.5;endArrow=classic;startArrow=classic;strokeColor=#B45309;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=10;fontColor=#B45309;dashed=1;" value="consulta sessão">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="a-map-frame" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#F9FAFB;strokeColor=#9CA3AF;fontSize=12;fontStyle=1;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=12;spacingTop=8;" value="Mapeamento subcomponente → código do Adaptive Delivery" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="80" y="890" width="1490" height="240" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="a-map-text" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=left;fontSize=11;fontColor=#374151;spacingLeft=20;spacingTop=10;" value="• Receptor de Sintoma — lib/adaptation-engine.ts → getRecommendations() / rankCategories(scores) (entrada da fase)&#xa;• Filtro de Resíduos — rankCategories: Object.entries(scores).filter(([, s]) =&gt; s &gt; 0.01) — descarta cauda de decaimento&#xa;• Ordenador (Ranking) — sort([, a], [, b]) =&gt; b - a — ranking decrescente; atribui rank = 1..N&#xa;• Detector de Destaque — highlighted = score &gt;= HIGHLIGHT_THRESHOLD (2.0) — flag usada pelo CategoryPills para realce visual&#xa;• Complementador — for catKey of DEFAULT_CATEGORY_ORDER: adiciona categorias sem score ao final (RN05 — acesso livre, vitrine completa)&#xa;• Consultor da Base — lib/session-repository.ts → findLatestSession(sessionId): SELECT ... ORDER BY event_timestamp DESC LIMIT 1&#xa;• Emissor de Diagnóstico — return CategoryRecommendation[] — consumido pelo Planejador (lib/cross-sell.ts) e pela API GET /recommendations&#xa;&#xa;Constantes (Knowledge): HIGHLIGHT_THRESHOLD=2.0 · score-floor=0.01 · DEFAULT_CATEGORY_ORDER=[PROMOCOES, LANCHES, PIZZAS, BEBIDAS, SALGADOS, DOCES, SOBREMESAS, CAFES, ACOMPANHAMENTOS, MOLHOS]" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="100" y="920" width="1450" height="200" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
